"intervals."
msgstr ""

#: includes/abprf_layout.php:669
msgid ""
"Note: You can set the cutoff date for allowing bookings in the next month. "
"By default, users can make bookings for the current month up to the 10th. "
"After this date, next month’s rental slots will become available for booking."
msgstr ""

